  "design_notes": "The chart is built for a medium difficulty, matching the energy contour closely. The intro has sparse quarter and half note taps. Once the drop hits at bar 4 (beat 16), the steps structure intensifies with consistent 8th-note streams, light crossovers, and hold freezes matching key sustained vocal and synth lines. The longest hold of 7 beats is placed during the high energy drop in S5. The outro scales down nicely to comfortable steps, matching the fade-out of the song's energy.",
